      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "MISCELLANEOUS - INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Reference is made to the memorandum captioned",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "as above dated June 10, 1952, from Mr. [REDACTED] to Mr. Belmont,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "which requested that OSI be contacted to determine if they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "turned over negatives of photographs of flying discs taken",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "by the above-captioned individual to Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "who works for Drew Pearson.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Lieutenant Colonel [REDACTED] and Lieutenant",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Colonel [REDACTED] of OSI were both contacted and both",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "advised that no inquiries had been received by OSI from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "[REDACTED].",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "The Bureau's Air Force Liaison Representative then",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "contacted Colonel [REDACTED] of Air Force Intelligence (A-2)",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "who likewise advised that no inquiries had been received by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "the Office of the Director of Intelligence from [REDACTED] or",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "anyone in Pearson's office. It is noted that matters involving",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "flying discs are handled by A-2. Colonel [REDACTED] advised that",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "it was possible that any inquiries made by Drew Pearson's office",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "would be made to the Office of the Public Information Officer",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "of the Air Force. However, Colonel [REDACTED] contacted the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Public Information Office, and he was advised that no inquiries",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "had been received from Drew Pearson's office regarding",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "flying discs and no photographs or negatives of photographs",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "of flying discs had ever been furnished to Drew Pearson's",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "office.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Colonel [REDACTED] advised that ordinarily when information",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "regarding flying discs is received by Air Force representatives",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "in the field, the information is referred to the Air Technical",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Intelligence Center, Wright-Patterson Air Force Base, Dayton,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
